**Verified positives**: `setMainView` exists in store with `'list'` valid (`store.ts:309-310`); `containerRef`/`ResizeObserver` move is correct (wrapper div is always rendered); popover `top-16` → `top-4` reposition is consistent with the new container scope; no primitive duplication; no drive-by changes (Polecat scope discipline ✓); GraphView is genuinely uncovered by `e2e/visual.spec.ts`, so PR's "no graph-specific tests" claim is accurate (pre-existing gap, not introduced here).
